data.description: Welcome to your beautiful custom home located in a highly desirable area!  Over 2400 sqft of living space with 4 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, primary bed downstairs, 4th bedroom upstairs could be used as a bonus room, landing area perfect for an office or sitting room, gorgeous engineered hardwood floors throughout the main level, & cathedral ceiling! Enjoy the warmth from your wood-burning fireplace as you entertain your family & friends, spacious formal dining room & breakfast nook compliment your lovely kitchen featuring white cabinets, stainless steel appliances, exquisite granite countertops, bathrooms include half bath downstairs for your guests, primary bath features large vanity with double sinks & an oversized tub with tile surround, full bath with tub/shower combo upstairs!  This home is perfect for your family's outdoor activities with a screened-in porch, fenced back yard, concrete driveway, & an oversized 2-car garage!  Perfectly nestled at the end of the street in a cul-de-sac.
